  <steps>
    <step order="1">Invoke `dataverse-create-schema` skill — review the Web API + PowerShell pattern for adding fields not coverable by PAC CLI.</step>
    <step order="2">Confirm current state of `sprk_analysisplaybook` via Dataverse describe — verify the 4 target fields do NOT exist (avoid duplicate-create error).</step>
    <step order="3">Create `sprk_lastindexedat` as DateTimeAttributeMetadata (DateAndTime format, UserLocal behavior, nullable).</step>
    <step order="4">Create global option-set `sprk_indexstatus` (or local picklist) with 5 values: 'not-indexed' (default), 'pending', 'indexed', 'stale', 'failed'. Document each option's label + value.</step>
    <step order="5">Create `sprk_indexstatus` (PicklistAttributeMetadata or ChoiceAttribute) wired to the option-set; default = 'not-indexed'.</step>
    <step order="6">Create `sprk_lastindexerror` as MemoAttributeMetadata (max length 500, format Text).</step>
    <step order="7">Create `sprk_indexhash` as StringAttributeMetadata (max length 64, format Text — sha256 hex string).</step>
    <step order="8">Publish all customizations (`PublishAllXml` Web API request).</step>
    <step order="9">Verify all 4 fields appear in Power Apps form designer for `sprk_analysisplaybook`.</step>
    <step order="10">Add all 4 fields to the unmanaged solution that contains `sprk_analysisplaybook` (or confirm they're already in the publisher's solution per ALM convention).</step>
    <step order="11">Update TASK-INDEX.md: task 030 → ✅; current-task.md → task 031 ready.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="Bash">PowerShell + Web API requests via `dataverse-create-schema` skill</tool>
    <tool name="Skill">dataverse-create-schema</tool>
    <tool name="Skill">dataverse-deploy (for solution export)</tool>
  </tools>

  <outputs>
    <output type="schema">sprk_analysisplaybook.sprk_lastindexedat (DateTime)</output>
    <output type="schema">sprk_analysisplaybook.sprk_indexstatus (Choice; 5 values)</output>
    <output type="schema">sprk_analysisplaybook.sprk_lastindexerror (Memo, max 500)</output>
    <output type="schema">sprk_analysisplaybook.sprk_indexhash (Text, max 64)</output>
    <output type="docs">notes/handoffs/030-schema-additions.md — field definitions + option-set values</output>
  </outputs>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">Dataverse describe of `sprk_analysisplaybook` shows all 4 new fields.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">`sprk_indexstatus` Choice has exactly 5 values matching spec.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Power Apps form designer can place all 4 fields on `sprk_analysisplaybook` main form.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Solution export ZIP contains all 4 field definitions.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Existing 6 production-bound playbooks remain functional (default `sprk_indexstatus = 'not-indexed'`).</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    Wave 2-A is sequential due to shared entity + Dataverse PUBLISH ALL behavior. After 030 publishes, task 031 adds the 5th field. Do not run 030 + 031 in parallel.
  </notes>

